<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Late Cancellation Notice</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-family:
      Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; } .email-container { max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #eee;
      border-left: 4px solid #E27A82; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; }
      .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; } .header img {
      max-height: 40px; display: block; margin: 0 auto 10px; } .fallback-logo {
      color: #E27A82; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; } .title { font-size:
      20px; font-weight: bold; color: #E27A82; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align:
      center; } .email-body { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; } .email-body
      ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; } .email-body ul li { margin-bottom:
      10px; } .email-body a { color: #0066cc; text-decoration: underline;
      word-break: break-word; } .button-link { display: block; width:
      fit-content; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #E27A82 !important;
      color: #ffffff !important; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none !important; text-align: center; font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold; } .button-link:hover { background-color: #c86a67
      !important; color: #ffffff !important; } .footer { font-size: 13px; color:
      #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 16px; } .alert-box { background-color: #fff3cd; border-left:
      4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Clickable Logo with Fallback -->
      <div class="header">
        <div style="height: 100px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
          <div class="fallback-logo">Fatima's Therapy Services</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="title">Late Cancellation Notice</div>

      <!-- Message -->
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear Admin,</p>

        <div class="alert-box">
          <p><strong>⚠️ Attention Required:</strong>
            A booking has been cancelled outside the allowed
            {{cancelCutoffDays}}-day notice period.</p>
        </div>

        <p>A session has been cancelled with the following details:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{booking.bookingId}}</li>
          <li><strong>Client:</strong> {{userName}}</li>
          <li><strong>Session Date:</strong> {{formattedDate}}</li>
          <li><strong>Cancellation Date:</strong> {{cancellationDate}}</li>
          <li><strong>Cancelled By:</strong>
            {{booking.cancellation.cancelledBy}}</li>
          <li><strong>Reason:</strong> {{booking.cancellation.reason}}</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Amount:</strong>
            {{payment.amount}}
            {{payment.paymentCurrency}}</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Status:</strong>
            {{payment.transactionStatus}}</li>
        </ul>

        <p>According to your policy, cancellations must be made at least
          {{cancelCutoffDays}}
          days before the appointment to be eligible for a refund.</p>

        {{#if isAdminCancelled}}
          <p><strong>Note:</strong>
            This appears to have been cancelled by admin. If this was you,
            please go ahead and issue a refund if appropriate.</p>
        {{else}}
          <p><strong>Note:</strong>
            Although clients shouldn't normally be able to cancel late through
            the interface, this cancellation was initiated by the client. Per
            your policy, a refund is not eligible, but you may still process one
            at your discretion.</p>
        {{/if}}

        <p>If you wish to process a refund:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Log in to your Safepay dashboard</li>
          <li>Find the transaction with reference:
            <strong>{{payment.transactionReferenceNumber}}</strong></li>
          <li>Process the refund through their interface</li>
        </ol>

        <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        &copy;
        {{currentYear}}
        Fatima's Therapy Services<br />
        This is an automated notification - please do not reply to this email.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>